Estimated Capacity = 20000 grams GaAs (Almost pure Gallium)

Energy cost spinning per gram = 18.5 kW-hrs/ 20000 grams [(Energy cost)/(Capacity)]


Energy cost spinning per gram = .000925 kW-hrs/g


